verbose_text: The expression levels of Bax, Bad, and caspase-3/-8 were partially upregulated and Bcl-2 and Bcl-xL expression levels were reduced, by MALAT1 siRNA administration in I/R-runners (I/R-runners + MALAT1 siRNA vs. I/R-runners + MALAT1 scrambled siRNA; P < 0.05).
